    <briefdescription>
<para>Network buffer representation. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This struct is used to represent network buffers. Such buffers are normally defined through the NET_BUF_POOL_*_DEFINE() APIs and allocated using the <ref refid="group__net__buf_1ga534366f3b5c7f41a28372c12149ca005" kindref="member">net_buf_alloc()</ref> API. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
